sentences: Scott Froml (born 21 August 1987), better known by his stage name Kerser,  is an Australian rapper.

He has released two mixtapes and several albums since 2009 and his second album No Rest for the Sickest reached No. 15 on the ARIA albums chart, while the album's tour DVD debuted at No. 1 on the ARIA Music DVD chart in 2013.
